title: Benihana offers Lobster & Shrimp Gyoza with six dumplings
statement: Benihana serves Lobster & Shrimp Gyoza consisting of six dumplings filled with lobster and shrimp, wrapped in pumpkin gyoza skin, served with ponzu lime sauce.

citations.quote: LOBSTER & SHRIMP GYOZA Six dumplings filled with lobster and shrimp, wrapped in pumpkin gyoza skin, served with ponzu lime sauce.
